Wenger on Alexis' future: &quot;The team selection has nothing to do with the transfer market. I want him to stay because I believe he is a very important player for us&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger on Alexis: &quot;When he came on you could see he created danger straight away. You have to accept as well when you play so many games, &amp; Sanchez plays every game, that sometimes a breather in the middle of the season helps them a little bit&quot;
